Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Club AT-X採訪映像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「瑪利亞狂熱」劇中扮演宮前加奈子的真田麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「瑪利亞狂熱」劇中扮演祇堂鞠也的小林優
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「瑪利亞狂熱」劇中扮演茉莉花的井上麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「瑪利亞狂熱」第一話決定在AT-X先行放送了  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作為第一話的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天將就本片向大家進行簡單介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆直接劇透好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇透！劇透！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣透乾淨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:01:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天為了能讓大家更加深入瞭解本片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫入？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  橫入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將由我們三個來介紹片中看點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}「瑪利亞狂熱」講的是一個什麼樣的故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣的故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  感想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪算簡介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超絕  超刺激  愛情喜劇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把重要的東西漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合趣味少女和…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!YES!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超S  超S少年的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女裝超S少年的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超絕？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿蔔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒蘿蔔的事  絕對沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿蔔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超合金？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超合金？有超合金蘿蔔出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是蘿蔔片啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有會出來的感覺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有那麼一點那樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實蘿蔔是不會出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮演的宮前加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個超喜歡女孩子的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂百合趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事由她轉入天之妃女子學園後正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很有貴族女校風的學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡呢  我所扮演的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少女  一眼看去是美少女  實際上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小子  你搞什麼飛機」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的一個角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許正是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺優憑空就能演繹出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望優去演真人版  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  麥克風…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別的…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻里奈的話我聽著好高興  有種不得不加油的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來演真人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不大行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面請扮演我的女僕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是演傭人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛的茉莉花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說我在劇中總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是情緒低落的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血壓也比較低
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼特別的感情起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  又特別的毒舌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒舌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上經常是「母豬」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常被這樣罵…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你這傢伙」之類的不滿的話也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多話讓人覺得「這種話能說嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待本篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}飾演角色的感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子應該說是個節奏很快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說情緒變換很激烈的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺呢  真的扮演起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現與其說是女高中生  分明就是個大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思維回路似乎是男性的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像男孩子的那種「這女孩真可愛  哈哈」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但加奈子的這種言行  又讓大家覺得很親近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊喊著「真可愛」一邊一次一次地吐…噴鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是逆流了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡出來就錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有很多東西流出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多東西流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之飾演女孩子的感覺在漸漸變淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  飾演前後的感覺最不一樣的就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺加奈子的台詞量不是一般的多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺八成以上都是加奈子的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們十分的過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過更辛苦的要說是鞠也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺經常轉換角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來回來去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全相反的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子和女孩子的兩種角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得是個十分可愛  待人熱情的聖母型角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「搞什麼飛機啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再變回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咚」地一聲就變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再學了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才給大家學過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咣」地變過來  再變回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  一個經常像這樣得到大家幫助的祇堂鞠也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誕生在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個超有加奈子的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說呢  雖說是男性  卻扮成女性來欺騙大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標好多  這樣一比劃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員的人數都洩露了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是一個有很多工作人員的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂又好玩的現場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一個沒什麼起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就我一個很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也想進入這種氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「過來吧你」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到腳了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺  因為這是早上的錄製現場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上配音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能以早上那種低落的情緒進入現場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會那麼幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這反而是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  畢竟是早上的現場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  沒錯  就是早上拼命提高情緒後才進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我一兩句的台詞特別多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家說得正熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我在旁邊冒出一句「母豬」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是跟不上節奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己總覺得不該打亂這個氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說台詞的時候總是七上八下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣站在麥克風前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一邊想著  可不能拖大家後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七上八下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！  像這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的一個現場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種現場  真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都很感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}還有什麼其他角色登場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如同班的幸啊  弓弦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有奈奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐裡的隆顯姐姐  絢璃學姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿管老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿管老師  與那國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多可愛的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遍地都是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這學校裡只有美少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  讓我十分滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台詞裡也有一句
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子說過2-B的誰誰誰很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2-B的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰誰  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之大家都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  就像在樓梯間碰到的誰誰也很可愛…的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在說的這人得多迷女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且宿舍也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是女生宿舍  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一天24小時都很滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的監視之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  兩人是一個房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆是一個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是讓她吃了很大的苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是監視與被監視的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被男孩子摸到後會起蕁麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都是被鞠也誘惑  然後被摸  「蕁麻疹啊～」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不要～蕁麻疹啊～」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺話越說越亂了  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家被吸引後一定會看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「她們在說什麼啊  是什麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就明白了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢  讓人忍不住想去見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}錄音現場的氣氛如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場的氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我可以說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事  說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣  大家並排坐著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄音的時候我坐在正中間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊就是她們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們夾著她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們夾著她坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這個不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說有時會變  但基本是這樣三個人坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後旁邊會坐著其他的聲優
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都坐得很近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為錄音的都是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像在班裡大家嘰嘰喳喳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是女子學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很華麗的現場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美妙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是只有你們三位在炒氣氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題怎麼回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家今天絕對是…說出「今天」了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一言我一語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是氣氛特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先表現一下氣氛有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過節一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰那麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過確實是個歡樂的現場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺總是在笑呢  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得肯定能看到有意思的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就這樣起哄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像真田總是想著「會不會有啥捏他出現呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因為演的是加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺在錄音現場我的地位和劇中角色差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在給你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美姐加油  這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  我們都在給你打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}OPED的曲目是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HANAJI
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HANAJI
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  鼻血嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你這麼來一次呢  比如在搞活動的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾們也一起來這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡到這裡來這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是優噴得最壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  又踩到腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加入表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈要求把這動作加進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞美老師也希望大家也來一起這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必大家看到歌名可能會想這是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是如大家想的那樣  鼻血而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日語裡的這個單詞還有別的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一開始看到革命歌名的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會有人懷疑看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感覺就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HA  NA…JI？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JI？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會懷疑是不是BI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火？…啊不對  JI？這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻血一般不會被當作歌名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HA  NA  JI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JI的時候這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JI的時候這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一首超級激烈的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首很可愛的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請不要只注意這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子也很歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲風是很歡樂的  請一定要在活動的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能搞熱氣氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家一起來做這個動作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣大家能開心的話  我們也會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一首鮮明表現「瑪麗亞狂熱」世界的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓這首曲子能為全劇添彩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嚇死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微活躍一下氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是ED
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是由我們三個演唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱團  不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天之妃少女合唱團」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…團」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取了這麼棒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實是電子樂味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是翻唱Yellow Magic Orchestra的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫「給你，心跳。」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的角色會展示個性的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到點傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像茉莉花唱這首歌時發生了點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你搞得那麼故弄玄虛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感覺實在想像不到茉莉花會怎麼唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  就拼命想怎樣才像茉莉花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始打算唱得可愛些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可馬上就想  不對  這不是茉莉花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始的時候完全是被你們倆帶著走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來實在是不唱不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情的話開始時還有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來因為曲子太長  漸漸有點煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁也越來越小  這樣就稍微有點茉莉花的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後就是邊唱邊歎氣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「還沒完啊」那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來因為錄了兩遍  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部分被編輯成了啥樣我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家唱的時候確實都是很有個性的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望能讓那部分保留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}對觀眾們的寄語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  「瑪利亞狂熱」即將開始播放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說片子裡充滿了讓人眼花繚亂的劇情展開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家觀看時一定要緊盯著熒幕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連細微的地方也不要放過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有各位角色都很有個性  很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請找出自己喜歡的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起滿足吧  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位  「瑪利亞狂熱」可謂獨一無二  前所未有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是超絕  超棒的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很超絕  超刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家一定  一定不要被甩下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才得到工作人員同意了  這點程度的動作沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克風掉了可不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不要被甩下  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家扮演的角色也都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很帥  很有個性的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像鞠也就是  既有可愛的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有「你這百合女」這樣的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的角色也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能和大家一起品味「瑪利亞狂熱」的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後注意不要被甩掉  盡情享受片子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請大家關注本片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請請
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是扮演茉莉花的井上麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這是部刺激又快節奏的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微一不留神就會錯過很多情節
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請大家一定要睜大眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外離畫面一米以上觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部片子裡真是充滿了個性十足的女孩男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會有許多各式各樣性格的角色登場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請一定要懷著加奈子的那種情感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊  這孩子真可愛」這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然大家是不會噴鼻血的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也要像噴鼻血般氣勢十足地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊這樣  一邊觀看本片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「瑪利亞狂熱」今後也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧





